snippet.title: Songs of Travel Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re so happy to announce our new game: Songs of Travel. 

It’s a story about migration, hopes and dreams, and identity. 

Our characters are based on real people, and we hope you’ll listen to their incredible and inspiring stories.
